Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: jack-capture
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, liblo7, libsndfile1, libmp3lame0
Description: Record JACK audio output to a file
 Captures audio from any JACK port and writes it to a WAV, FLAC, or
 MP3 file. Useful for debugging and recording sessions on pi-Stomp.
